    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate discretization error control (GCI < 5%), satisfactory agreement with FDA benchmark experimental data (RH < 1 at all operating points), and appropriate relevance of validation activities to the COU. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device regulatory submission.",
